                "invention-title": [
                    "Production method of chromium-containing molten iron",
                    "含铬铁水的生产方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a production method of chromium-containing molten iron, which comprises the following steps: proportioning: proportioning chromium-iron pellets, flux and coke; charging: preheating the proportioned ferrochrome pellets, flux and coke, and then adding the preheated ferrochrome pellets, flux and coke into the submerged arc furnace from the top of the submerged arc furnace; the method comprises the following steps: smelting: introducing current into an electrode in a submerged arc furnace for smelting, and carrying out furnace charge pre-reduction in the smelting process, namely purifying submerged arc furnace gas discharged from the top of the submerged arc furnace in the smelting process, and adding hydrogen and coal bed gas to form mixed gas of the submerged arc furnace gas, the hydrogen and the coal bed gas, and after being heated, the mixed gas is uniformly sprayed into the submerged arc furnace from a tuyere below the furnace charge surface of the submerged arc furnace, and the furnace charge in the submerged arc furnace is pre-reduced. By utilizing the method provided by the invention, the chemical energy of the submerged arc furnace gas is fully utilized, and the furnace charge is pre-reduced by the submerged arc furnace gas, so that the consumption of coke during smelting of the submerged arc furnace is remarkably reduced, and the aim of low-carbon smelting is fulfilled."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种含铬铁水的生产方法，包括：配料，将铬铁球团、熔剂、焦炭进行配料；加料，将配料后的铬铁球团、熔剂、焦炭预热后从矿热炉炉顶加入到矿热炉内；冶炼，将矿热炉中的电极通入电流进行冶炼，其中，在冶炼过程中进行炉料预还原，炉料预还原包括：将冶炼过程中从矿热炉炉顶排出的矿热炉煤气净化后，配入氢气和煤层气，形成矿热炉煤气、氢气和煤层气的混合气，将混合气加热后从矿热炉料面下的风口均匀喷入矿热炉内，对矿热炉内的炉料进行预还原。利用本发明的方法，矿热炉煤气的化学能得到充分利用，并且通过将矿热炉煤气对炉料进行预还原，显著降低矿热炉冶炼时焦炭的消耗量，从而达成了低碳冶炼的目标。"
                }
